Page_0:
"To complete their initiation, aspirants to the
Dark Watch must drink of the blood of Yanapaw.
They shall stay in the Chamber of Passage for
three days until their skin has become as dark
and hard as ebony. Only those of worth can
withstand the pain of passage, all others will
perish within the very first day.

Existing between the dead and the living, 
members of the Dark Watch have the honor to
guard over the City of the Dead and ensure
safe travel to the stars for the deceased."